                  </hi>. I am Mrs. Platts' daughter. The prisoner took my mother's apartment—I know this bolster and candlestick to be my mother's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Can you prove that you know that candlestick? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, and I can bring the person who left it for arrears of rent.</p>
